{"tid":510918,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【最好的禮物】60年死黨　驗DNA驚覺是親兄弟","createTime":"2017-12-27T03:21:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-27T03:50:47.000Z","uid":39464,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e0334e9a752fa048c49b99f4a9e99a2f27237ace","tid":510918,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T03:21:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171227/s00005/d9fec9b6cc80bf1bece3d1d4bd3c1262.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171227%2Fs00005%2Fd9fec9b6cc80bf1bece3d1d4bd3c1262.jpg&h=b2955f6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這個故事如同電影般。兩名從小就是摯友的夏威夷男子，他們過去一直為了找尋自己的親生父母而各自想辦法，想不到兩人透過同一個網站尋親（<a href=\"http://Ancestry.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FAncestry.com&d=9XDN3Mps%2F8vLzcjwtXctS6MP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=d024e04a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Ancestry.com</a>），檢驗DNA後竟發現兩位「好兄弟」原來是「真兄弟」。兩個已一頭銀灰髮大男人，日前在派對上向親朋宣布這驚喜，相擁慶祝，直呼這是最好的聖誕禮物。<br />\n<br />\n羅賓遜（Alan Robinson）與麥法蘭（Walter Macfarlane）當了60年的朋友。他們都是在夏威夷出生，生日隔了15個月，是在6年級時相識，並在檀香山市預備學校一起玩美式足球。麥法蘭不知道自己的父親是誰，而羅賓遜是被人領養，不過他們各自都在尋找自己的身世。<br />\n<br />\n麥法蘭用了不同的方法尋親不果，<a href=\"http://最後選擇在Ancestry.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%9C%80%E5%BE%8C%E9%81%B8%E6%93%87%E5%9C%A8Ancestry.com&d=9XDN3Mps%2F8vLzcjwtXctS6MP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=608ef0a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">最後選擇在Ancestry.com</a>進行DNA測試，發現與他DNA最符合的人，叫Robi737。原來羅賓遜也使用相同網站尋找家人，他們最後得知親生母親是同一人。<br />\n<br />\n麥法蘭說：「這真的很令人震驚。」兩人選擇在23日晚在派對上向親朋好友公布他們是親生兄弟的關係。羅賓遜說：「這種經驗實在是難以形容，到現在還是非常激動。我不知道這種感覺多久後才會平復。」兩兄弟已打算一起旅行與享受退休生活。羅賓遜說：「這是最棒的聖誕禮物，根本想像不到。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171227/s00005/1514342278247\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171227%2Fs00005%2F1514342278247&d=9XDN3Mps%2F8vLzcjwtXctS6MP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=b6df81f3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171227%2Fs00005%2F1514342278247&h=1c0d3f8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171227/s00005/1514342278247</a>"},{"pid":"71a512399442b69c1b2a0681140d2e731a350be2","tid":510918,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T03:24:51.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"0c6ad35678f92ac4e8e396720cc493160a44a137","tid":510918,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T03:24:52.000Z","msg":"能成為密友大概總帶著愛"},{"pid":"843bbd8cd8acf5c9b5eed8dc25e767f6acb855b7","tid":510918,"uid":58536,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T03:26:43.000Z","msg":"咁佢老豆都幾仆街<br />\n棄完一個又一個"},{"pid":"fc1cbf4257b60ea1e09b781d411752571bdad3f2","tid":510918,"uid":1082,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"843bbd8cd8acf5c9b5eed8dc25e767f6acb855b7","tid":510918,"uid":58536,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T03:26:43.000Z","msg":"咁佢老豆都幾仆街<br />\n棄完一個又一個"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T03:34:57.000Z","msg":"老母同一個人黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"363e3a765afc3c2b4a213aec7bcd9a93d7a1a4e0","tid":510918,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T03:39:35.000Z","msg":"親兄弟...好似唔係咁解"},{"pid":"ba6f589999e09f42927f5e792a9a1d61d2c4f956","tid":510918,"uid":54181,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T03:40:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"71feb1067eab1d9e378725c04b8e710d04e48533","tid":510918,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T03:40:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁佢老豆都幾仆街<br />\n棄完一個又一個</blockquote>老母同一個人黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\